  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a relaxing farm RPG game where you can earn money by collecting and raising livestock! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with adorable villagers to increase your popularity in the village through chatting and giving gifts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please enjoy a cozy farm life in this small village!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/d8eb47511de973c088b77c5b2a31d558.avif?t=1762827632\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of livestock to harvest high-quality milk and eggs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The larger your farm, the more livestock you can raise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/7501ce6f4d68f5595eaa7b4c2e2fc1a4.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=702 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/7501ce6f4d68f5595eaa7b4c2e2fc1a4.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/7501ce6f4d68f5595eaa7b4c2e2fc1a4.mp4?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/15f7a66eedda30f2f33c6d7f89935b68.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=746 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/15f7a66eedda30f2f33c6d7f89935b68.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/15f7a66eedda30f2f33c6d7f89935b68.mp4?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your house by collecting materials and eventually own a luxurious mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0ca4943059378dd83c2704afb00cc30f.avif?t=1762827632\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▪️Game features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farm management RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No ultimate goal! Just enjoy a leisurely life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultivate relationships with villagers and become a family!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/2c4bc4d827ce6544816e85602edfcac8.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=392 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/2c4bc4d827ce6544816e85602edfcac8.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/2c4bc4d827ce6544816e85602edfcac8.mp4?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0835c5ae0f07024dc2ff63cb91c81f0b.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=634 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0835c5ae0f07024dc2ff63cb91c81f0b.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0835c5ae0f07024dc2ff63cb91c81f0b.mp4?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a relaxing farm RPG game where you can earn money by collecting and raising livestock! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with adorable villagers to increase your popularity in the village through chatting and giving gifts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please enjoy a cozy farm life in this small village!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/d8eb47511de973c088b77c5b2a31d558.avif?t=1762827632\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of livestock to harvest high-quality milk and eggs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The larger your farm, the more livestock you can raise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/7501ce6f4d68f5595eaa7b4c2e2fc1a4.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=702 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/7501ce6f4d68f5595eaa7b4c2e2fc1a4.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/7501ce6f4d68f5595eaa7b4c2e2fc1a4.mp4?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/15f7a66eedda30f2f33c6d7f89935b68.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=746 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/15f7a66eedda30f2f33c6d7f89935b68.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/15f7a66eedda30f2f33c6d7f89935b68.mp4?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your house by collecting materials and eventually own a luxurious mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0ca4943059378dd83c2704afb00cc30f.avif?t=1762827632\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▪️Game features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farm management RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No ultimate goal! Just enjoy a leisurely life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultivate relationships with villagers and become a family!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/2c4bc4d827ce6544816e85602edfcac8.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=392 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/2c4bc4d827ce6544816e85602edfcac8.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/2c4bc4d827ce6544816e85602edfcac8.mp4?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0835c5ae0f07024dc2ff63cb91c81f0b.poster.avif?t=1762827632\" width=634 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0835c5ae0f07024dc2ff63cb91c81f0b.webm?t=1762827632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420240/extras/0835c5ae0f07024dc2ff63cb91c81f0b.m